Due to the recent rain and the resulting soggy conditions of the grass areas at Art Wright Stadium and Memorial Park, the parking plan for tomorrow’s (11/1) home football game against Brecksville-Broadview Heights will need to be altered. The new plan is as follows:

- All parking on the south side of Art Wright Stadium will be closed;
- The north parking lot at Art Wright Stadium will be available for those who require handicap parking;
- All other spectators are asked to park at Wadsworth High School (625 Broad St.); and
- Beginning at 5:00 p.m. and continuing throughout the evening, we will run shuttle buses between the student parking lot at Wadsworth High School and Art Wright Stadium.

